'''WTAI'''

(internet) Wireless Telephone Applications Interface - The Wireless Telephone Applications Interface (WTAI) can be used in conjunction with the Wireless Application Protocol ([[WAP]]).  WAP is an open international standard for applications that use wireless communication, this allows text based web pages on small mobile devices.  The Wireless Telephone Application Interface allows a phone number to be linked to a a WAP page.  

For example

<a href="wtai://wp/mc;12341234">12341234</a>

